==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒk|-ɒk]]

=== Noun ===
'''mock'''
# an [[imitation]], usually connotation is one of lesser quality
# mockery, the act of mocking

==== Translations ====
*Dutch: [[imitatie]]
*German: [[Nachahmung]] ''f''
*Japanese: [[偽の]] (にせの, nise-no), [[擬似の]] (ぎじの, giji-no)
*Portuguese: [[simulado]]

=== Verb ===
'''to mock''' ([[mocks]], [[mocked]], [[mocking]])

# to [[mimic]], to [[simulate]]
# to make fun of by mimicking, to [[taunt]]
# to disappoint someone

